title: "ALS Connectome Degeneration Project"
version: 2.0.0
date-released: 2026-06-08
url: "https://github.com/MaryamRezaeeNl/als-connectome"
doi: 10.5281/zenodo.20592681
abstract: "Computational study of ALS-like cascade dynamics
  on the C. elegans motor connectome (61 neurons, 127 synapses).
  Multi-phase simulation framework covering criticality emergence,
  therapeutic windows, disease subtypes, and pre-symptomatic
  early-warning signals."
keywords:
  - neurodegeneration
  - connectome
  - ALS
  - computational neuroscience
  - tipping points
  - C. elegans
